            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "In my code, I didn't specify the `language_level=3` directive.\r\nAttaching the debugger showed `is_python3_source` was `False`, and it went to `_append_escape_sequence` (from line 941) even when `is_raw` was set.\r\n\r\nThe problem I faced is resolved, so I'll close the issue.\r\nThanks!",
